Thanks for the bailout, bro.

1115
01:07:51.338 --> 01:07:53.073
Wouldn't be
the first time.

1116
01:07:53.541 --> 01:07:54.576
Is that
what this is about?

1117
01:07:55.108 --> 01:07:56.376
Is this about what?

1118
01:07:58.813 --> 01:08:00.080
It is, isn't it?

1119
01:08:01.281 --> 01:08:02.684
You're still mad
about what I did.

1120
01:08:03.851 --> 01:08:06.286
Do you know
who I did it for?

