and feel like a failure.

1145
01:08:57.572 --> 01:08:59.206
-Jackson!
-No, you listen.

1146
01:08:59.238 --> 01:09:01.375
That's all she said,
all the time.

1147
01:09:01.408 --> 01:09:02.777
You're perfect
and I'm not.

1148
01:09:02.810 --> 01:09:04.277
You saved me.

1149
01:09:04.310 --> 01:09:05.680
And I should have been
the one in jail.

1150
01:09:05.712 --> 01:09:06.781
Not you. Me.

1151
01:09:09.282 --> 01:09:10.818
